{"tid":666791,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"破巴塞不敗身 累利迷停止手淫49年","createTime":"2018-05-16T07:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T08:09:02.000Z","uid":54373,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a54d1b10cc85570c6042ea9221497fd18ffb268b","tid":666791,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:29:58.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=71H6aUdLW1dRq8EZX0xA2Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=03e75f00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】利雲特球迷早前於twitter揚言，若果球隊能於西甲打破巴塞隆拿的不敗身，便會停止手淫的自娛行為，結果求仁得仁。<br />\n<br />\n1名西甲下游隊伍利雲特的粉絲，在球隊周日迎戰應屆西甲冠軍巴塞隆拿的西甲之前，可能覺得利雲特不太可能擊退巴塞，竟於twitter許下「有味」承諾。<br />\n<br />\n這位利雲特球迷指，愛隊若然勇挫巴塞，便會暫時戒掉手淫的發洩習慣，而實際停止時間，將以貼文獲得網民留言回應的數目去決定，1個回應便停止1日，如此類推。<br />\n<br />\n結果，利雲特真的爆大冷，一度領先5:1下，最終以5:4打破巴塞今季聯賽的不敗金身！這名利雲特球迷求仁得仁，也是時候找數。<br />\n<br />\n這個「有味」貼文在比賽未完已有多達1.8萬個花生友回應，換言之，當事人需要暫停手淫行為超過49年！<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"e7aa3ada8492b2980558fda47aa0e79267040ff1","tid":666791,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:33:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1c78f410d942c0ab6c7890e07575b93d18cbe3","tid":666791,"uid":5843,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:34:00.000Z","msg":"王騎試下歐聯決賽咁樣燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e7e5b797d785c930640ae5c551ba30b0426e33","tid":666791,"uid":170910,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:40:30.000Z","msg":"睇標題心諗關利物浦咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b26a8eef156180f41ff43984ede6c510f8b591","tid":666791,"uid":54551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9d1c78f410d942c0ab6c7890e07575b93d18cbe3","tid":666791,"uid":5843,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:34:00.000Z","msg":"王騎試下歐聯決賽咁樣燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:45:47.000Z","msg":"王騎最好快啲打埋最後啲飛機佢"},{"pid":"ea31e9e579f0d3d828f2babbe5e78eefd670d336","tid":666791,"uid":33058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:50:31.000Z","msg":"叫條女扑未得囉, 有乜所謂"},{"pid":"3b5db230dbb39c8b0b81d613a484e0c32fd83adc","tid":666791,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:51:32.000Z","msg":"我出返去先"},{"pid":"e39a4db57dc7508126a750a99e6f9fababd1003b","tid":666791,"uid":18638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:54:53.000Z","msg":"用飛機杯咪得"},{"pid":"96f6111cdda92bba2ba35b1624da01a4693292a7","tid":666791,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抵死，不過偷偷地打都無人會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f370186ea14e3cdce8f000282eaa5d255ae49d1","tid":666791,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:09:02.000Z","msg":"好彩係利雲特唔係利狗，利狗最叻打飛機<br />\n唔比佢地打真係谷精上腦死晒"}]}